@echo off\n\n:: Try to add a value with a symbol (#) to the MRUList\nreg add "HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\RunMRU" /v "#" /t REG_SZ /d "C:\Windows\notepad.exe" /f\nreg add "HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\RunMRU" /v MRUList /t REG_SZ /d "a b c #"\n\n:: Verify the MRUList value\nreg query "HKCU\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\RunMRU" /v MRUList